    .desc = Forged for the elite forces of the Royal Crown Marines, the sleek, tempered construction of this blade has been lauded by its wielders.
ent-RMCTantoB = MK3 infantry service tanto
    .desc = Forged for the elite forces of the Royal Crown Marines, the sleek, tempered construction of this blade has been lauded by its wielders.
