    .desc = This thin, yet rigid dagger is favored for its combination of elegant features and lethality in hand-to-hand combat.
ent-RMCSawtoothDaggerB = Fiore-Pattern trench dagger
    .desc = This thin, yet rigid dagger is favored for its combination of elegant features and lethality in hand-to-hand combat.
